  "question": "Who are Anakin Skywalker's children?",
  "answer": "In both canon and Legends, Anakin Skywalker had twin children with Padmé Amidala:\n\n- **Luke Skywalker**\n- **Leia Organa** (born Leia Amidala Skywalker)\n\nThey were born in 19 BBY at the secret Polis Massa base, shortly before Padmé's death. To protect them from the Sith, the twins were separated — Luke was raised on Tatooine by his step-uncle and aunt, Owen and Beru Lars, while Leia was raised on Alderaan by the royal House of Organa.",
